Apply by phone
You can also choose to apply for Global Investment Centre by phone – although note it will take longer to complete your application as we’ll have to send your documents by post.
Call us on 03456 076180*



The Global Investment Centre is offered without advice, on an execution only basis. HSBC is not required to assess the suitability of this service for you, which means that the protection offered by the Financial Conduct Authority's rules on assessing suitability will not apply. If you have any doubts about whether this service is suitable for your needs, you should seek advice from a Financial Adviser (you may be charged for any advice you receive).
Please note online trades through the Global Investment Centre are limited to £99,999. If you would like to place a trade of £100,000 or more, you may do so by phone – please call us on 03456 076180*.
* Our opening hours are Monday to Friday 8.00am to 6.00pm (excluding Bank Holidays). Textphone: 08457 660 391.
To help us continually improve our service, and in the interests of security, we may monitor and/or record your communications with us.












