The Global Investment Centre is offered without advice, on an execution only basis. HSBC is not required to assess the suitability of this service for you, which means that the protection offered by the Financial Conduct Authority’s rules on assessing suitability will not apply. If you have any doubts about whether this service is suitable for your needs, you should seek advice from a Financial Adviser (you may be charged for any advice you receive).
Check if you qualify for adviceIf you have £50,000 or more in savings and investments, you may be eligible for HSBC Premier Financial Advice. See the full eligibility criteria.


